   emission and Kalbach systematic angular distr.                 6231 1451
   (code PCROSS by R.Capote et al)                                6231 1451
 - Hybrid Monte Carlo preequilibrium model(M.Blann)               6231 1451
   (code DDHMS by M.Chadwick, mod. by B.V.Carlson)                6231 1451
 - Complete gamma-ray cascade after emission of                   6231 1451
   each particle, including realistic treatment of                6231 1451
   discrete transitions                                           6231 1451
 - Access to OM segment of the RIPL library [RIPL]                6231 1451
 - Built-in input parameter files, such as masses,                6231 1451
   level density, discrete levels, fission barriers               6231 1451
   and gamma strength functions based on the RIPL                 6231 1451
   library [RIPL]                                                 6231 1451
 - Automatic retrieval of experimental data from the              6231 1451
   EXFOR library                                                  6231 1451
 - ENDF-6 formatting (code EMPEND by A.Trkov)                     6231 1451
   coupled to graphical presentation capabilities                 6231 1451
   (code ZVView by V. Zerkin) through the chain of                6231 1451
   PrePro codes by D. Cullen                                      6231 1451
 - ENDF checking codes (CHECKR, FIZCON, PSYCHE)                   6231 1451
 - Highly automated fitting of optical model                      6231 1451
   parameters (by B.V. Carlson)                                   6231 1451
 - KALMAN code for fitting experimental data and                  6231 1451
 - generating covariances                                         6231 1451
 - Support for NJOY                                               6231 1451
